Installation:
  - Extract the content of the plugin into <gosa home>/plugins/authorizations
  - Edit gosa.conf:
    - Add <tab class="authorizationsManagement" name="Authorizations" /> into the <usertabs> tag
    - Add <tab class="authorizationsManagement" name="Authorizations" /> into the <MyAccountTabs> tag
  - Create the authorizations.xml configuration file based on authorizations.xml.sample
